headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires DMc Insurance Partners
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Austin, Texas-based Howe Insurance Group LLC, dba DMc Insurance Partners. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires M.J. Schuetz Insurance Services Inc.
